text: haey puok del daohsa knongchamnaom puok areab chonobt ban mk chuob( mou ham meat) daembi som keat aoy anounhnhat dl puokke( mintow thveusangkream) . haey puok del ban phout kohk a l laoh ning anak noam sar robsa trong ban angkouy nowphteah( yeang prohaen daoy minban mk som karoanounhnhat pi mou ham meat) . puok del ban brachheang knongchamnaom puokke nung trauv ttuol tearounakamm yeang chhucheab
